            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d87fd045-a8e7-4248-9dda-3314cc29ce10">
                Mr. Sandys
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d87fd045-a8e7-4248-9dda-3314cc29ce10" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
