<p class="">It only needs a few spots to cost a large amount of money.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-4b1c82c0-ded4-44aa-9a33-e27c2ee5d7a7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
